{
  "stem": "3380.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We used to sleep in a farmhouse or in-- or in the field in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were-- next day we have to continuously to march.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, one day that was-- and I-- I think it was exactly eight days, in the morning a SS guy what worked in the-- an SS man that worked in the kitchen in Jaworzno, he used to came back with the motorcycle and he said, where do you want to go?",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You going to go to [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oppeln, ?] a city in Germany?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oppeln ?] is by the-- is occupied by the Soviets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is no use going there because the Soviets are there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they start looking up the plans, the maps, and find out, and they told us to make a left turn through fields, and they start chasing us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they start using machine guns, you know, machine guns, and they used to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whoever fell, fell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had to run like cattle, and lots of people died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Lots of people were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the morning, early in the morning, we got in in a camp, but the camp was also part of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called it Blechhammer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Blechhammer, at that time, was in process of being liquidated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The people already had their portions, and they start marching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the SS men told us whoever wants to remain should remain, and whoever feels like walking with them can walk with them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As far as we are concerned, it did not make any difference.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if you're going to march, that's going to be the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And let them do whatever-- it's-- they're-- going to happen, it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
